    "The scope of this survey is limited to the available literature and may overlook emerging trends or unpublished findings.",
    "3) While we provide a taxonomy of LLM applications in psychotherapy, this framework may not fully encompass the complexity of real-world clinical settings or the diverse range of therapeutic approaches currently in practice.",
